          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The filter computes the luminance of each pixel",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and uses it to define the opacity of the result, combined",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "with black (zero) color components.",
              "type": "text"
